http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/kolkata/3-of-family-found-dead-in-Kolkata-flat/article14001541.ece

Three members of a family were found dead on Saturday inside an apartment in south Kolkata's Palm Avenue area.“The dead have been identified as Jessica Fonseca and her two sons - Tarren and Joshua. The fourth person Neil Fonseca, husband of Jessica, is in a hospital with serious injuries,” Debasish Boral, Special Additional Commissioner of Kolkata Police (Crime), told The Hindu.Mr. Boral said senior officers are at the crime scene and investigations have been started to ascertain cause of the crime.Preliminary findings indicate that a family dispute could have resulted in the murder. Senior police officers are awaiting the statement of Neil Fonseca, once his condition improves.